TEE ENEA EMPIRE BREAKOUT STRATEGY

1. MARKETS: Forex (London/NY), Gold, Indices
   HTF: H4/H1 bias | LTF: M15/M5 entry

2. STRUCTURE: HH+HL (bull) OR LL+LH (bear)
   No bias = NO TRADE

3. SETUP:
   A. Tight consolidation range
   B. Liquidity sweep (fakeout wick + rejection)

4. ENTRY:
   Break → Strong close → Retest → Confirmation candle

5. CONFIRMATION: Engulfing, momentum, or rejection wick

6. RISK:
   SL: Below HL (bull)/above LH (bear)
   TP: 1R partial → Prior structure → Major level
   RR: Min 1:2 (prefer 1:3+)
   Risk: 1% max per trade

7. TIMING: London Open, NY Open, NY Killzone

8. CHECKLIST:
   ✔ HTF bias      ✔ Consolidation  
   ✔ Liquidity sweep ✔ Strong breakout close
   ✔ Retest confirmed ✔ RR ≥1:2

AVOID: Every breakout, no bias, no sweep, chasing
